{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十四回\"料事如神\"主要讲述胡铁花在沙漠中被白衣人（石观音门下弟子）放走后，发现楚留香和姬冰雁留下的物品，包括极乐之星、丝巾、判官笔等。琵琶公主突然出现，与胡铁花展开一段充满火药味的对话。胡铁花发现琵琶公主对楚留香的丝巾非常在意，故意用楚留香的话刺激她，导致琵琶公主大哭。胡铁花最终道歉，两人关系缓和。章节展现了胡铁花的豪爽直率、琵琶公主的娇蛮任性，以及楚留香在暗处的影响。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人为财死，鸟为食亡，但这……这又何苦?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你害怕了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怕什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然是怕我杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看我像个怕死的人么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你面上虽在充英雄，心里还是有些害怕的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂!你莫忘了，这些东西是拿来和你们交换那'极乐之星'的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想将极乐之星带回去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然想带回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你凭什么以为我不会杀你?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我死也得将极乐之星带回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒怪了，一个死人又怎能将东西带得回去?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好好地照顾他们",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看情况，他只怕又是被酒害的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若不死在酒上，那才是怪事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他很好，他不怕死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不怕死就很好么?呆子和白痴都是不怕死的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不怕死的，总比怕死的好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两人争论什么，这次他一定死不了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你凭什么以为别人不敢杀他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她若将小胡杀了，又叫谁将那极乐之星带回去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知她要小胡将东西带回去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若没有人将极乐之星带回去，又怎能骗得那位糊涂王爷说出秘密呢?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只怕也就是惟一的好处了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来老臭虫到这里来过，却怎知他为何又要易容改扮?瞧他用的颜色又黄又黑，他莫非是被女人追怕了，所以改扮成个丑八怪?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小木瓶，黑珍珠和丝巾自然是老臭虫的，但巾上绣着的这'曲'字又是谁呢?莫非……莫非……是那位多情公主的闺名么?……哈!老臭虫真有一手，三下两下，就让人家女孩子将定情物都送给他了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "判官笔、鼻烟壶、钥匙、银刀和金珠却必定是那死公鸡的了，他这人真婆婆妈妈得和女人一样，连钥匙都带在身上，难道还怕别人等他走了后，就开他的房门，偷他的东西么——嘿嘿!看来他倒该改个名字，叫小气鬼了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人既已聚在一起，天塌下来也能接得住，我还为他们担心什么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道老臭虫又找到了新人?但纵然如此，他也不会要人家肚兜呀!老臭虫怎么会变得如此肉麻?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好香。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来我们这位道貌岸然的姬先生，还是位多情种子呢!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多情总比无情的好，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "堂堂的胡大英雄，怎地也变得如此胆小了?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是你，你不在家弹琵琶，跑到这里来干什么?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琵琶若无知音欣赏，还是不弹的好。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不弹琵琶，你就没有别的事可做了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是草包，你又是什么?绣花枕头么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你用不着对我发威，这话又不是我说的，你若不服气，不会去找说这话的人算账么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕你见着她时，连话都说不出了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你用不着再解释，反正我知道你有这毛病，每次都要偷偷摸摸的来见人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也用不着总是对我发威，难道我有什么地方惹着了你么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就算没有嫁给你，你也不必一见我面就生气呀!",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若总是对我这样，就证明你还是偷偷爱着我的，所以你才会因为我不嫁给你而生气，你才会吃那老臭虫的醋。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像你这样的女子，若真嫁给我了，我不被活活气死才怪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃不到葡萄，就说葡萄酸，真没出息。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么冷的天，若不喝杯酒挡挡寒气，只怕就要冻成死鱼了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若有人想以酒来气我，那才大错而特错，我刚刚上了喝酒的当，现在简直一看见酒就头疼。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这酒可当真不错，一喝下去全身都暖和了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女孩子家喝酒居然喝得啧啧发响，真没规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是要没规矩，这样才能让有规矩的人气死。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你这手巾是哪里来的?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捡来的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快……快还给我。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还给你?为何要还给你?难道是你的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是……是我的又怎样?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒奇怪了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么奇怪?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明明听见那老臭虫说：'那母夜叉自作多情，还以为我会将这破布好好保存哩!'你难道就是那母夜叉不成?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁!你……你简直不是人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又何必对我发威，这话又不是我说的，你要是不服气，难道不会去找说这话的人么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕你真的见着那人时，连话都说不出来了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他……他为何将我送他的东西随便乱抛?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只因……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，随便你怎么骂我都没关系，只求你莫要再哭了，好么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若承认你是个特级混账，我就不哭了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我岂非早已承认了……唉!",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然承认，为何还叹气?难道不甘愿么?",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我心甘情愿，承认我是个大混蛋，这样好了么……哈!错就错在我是个男人，男人骂女人就是混蛋，女人就算骂男人是大草包也没关系，因为女人会哭，这本事男人可不大容易学会的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么?你再说一遍。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我说男人都是混蛋，女人都是好蛋……都是好人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话还差不多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    }
